OL,7,FTelevision gambling ads significantly
OL,8,Finfluenced betting activity during the
OL,9,F2022 Fifa World Cup, raising concerns
OL,10,Fahead of this year's event, according
OL,11,Fto a study.
OL,13,FThe findings suggest current rules
OL,14,Fgoverning gambling ads may be
OL,15,F"insufficient" to protect those most
OL,16,Fat risk, academics from the University
OL,17,Fof Sheffield warned.
