OL,3,CTV gambling ads significantly
OL,4,Cinfluenced betting on 2022 Fifa World
OL,5,CCup ` study
OL,7,FThe study examined betting behaviour
OL,8,Famong men aged between 18 and 45 in
OL,9,FEngland during the 2022 tournament in
OL,10,FQatar, to see how exposure to gambling
OL,11,Fads on TV influenced the likelihood of
OL,12,Fthem placing bets.
OL,14,FIt found that the frequency of
OL,15,Ffootball betting was between 16% and
OL,16,F24% higher during matches broadcast on
OL,17,Fchannels screening gambling ads
OL,18,Fcompared with games shown on channels
OL,19,Fthat did not screen them.
