OL,5,CCup ` study
OL,7,FLead author of the study and research
OL,8,Fassociate at the University of
OL,9,FSheffield's School of Medicine and
OL,10,FPopulation Health, Ellen McGrane,
OL,11,Fsaid: "These television adverts may be
OL,12,Facting as powerful triggers during
OL,13,Flive games, encouraging betting even
OL,14,Famong people who had no prior
OL,15,Fintention to gamble.
OL,17,F"One of our key findings was that this
OL,18,Fadvertising doesn't simply shift
OL,19,Fpeople between betting platforms, it
OL,20,Fincreases the overall amount of
OL,21,Fgambling taking place.
