OL,7,F"A substantial body of evidence shows
OL,8,Fthat when gambling participation rises
OL,9,Fat a population level, gambling-
OL,10,Frelated harm also increases,
OL,11,Fsuggesting that the current
OL,12,Frestrictions in place may not be
OL,13,Feffective enough.
