OL,7,FA Betting and Gaming spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "Millions of adults enjoy a
OL,9,Fflutter during major sporting events
OL,10,Flike the World Cup, with the vast
OL,11,Fmajority doing so safely, supported by
OL,12,Fstrong protections in place in the
OL,13,Fregulated sector.
