OL,5,CCup ` study
OL,7,F"The evidence shows that advertising
OL,8,Fby licensed bookmakers is actually
OL,9,Ffalling, reducing by 1.7% year-on-year
OL,10,Fsince 2021. It now makes up just 2.7
OL,11,Fper cent of total UK advertising, with
OL,12,F20% of advertising focused on safer
OL,13,Fgambling messaging. This decline has
OL,14,Fcontinued during major football events
OL,15,Fsuch as Euro 2024, when the number of
OL,16,Fgambling adverts shown per day was 20%
OL,17,Flower than during the World Cup in
OL,18,F2022.
