OL,7,F"Bookmakers already face some of the
OL,8,Ftoughest ad rules anywhere and
OL,9,Fvoluntarily introduced the whistle-to-
OL,10,Fwhistle ban, which has cut the number
OL,11,Fof TV betting adverts seen by kids
OL,12,Fduring live sport by 97% at that time.
OL,14,F"The real danger comes from harmful
OL,15,Fillegal gambling sites, which flood
OL,16,Fthe internet with ads, carry out no
OL,17,Fage checks and offer no protections."
